135
00:12:00,607 --> 00:12:01,407
That's right

136
00:12:01,541 --> 00:12:03,643
The principals
are assembling in an hour

137
00:12:03,776 --> 00:12:04,878
See you then

138
00:12:05,411 --> 00:12:06,779
