143
00:12:18,958 --> 00:12:20,860
We're in here

144
00:12:23,363 --> 00:12:25,098
Jesus Christ, guys

145
00:12:25,231 --> 00:12:26,366
What the hell is Kruschev thinking?

146
00:12:26,399 --> 00:12:28,902
Did you have any indication of this
from your KGB pal, Bolshakov?

147
00:12:29,068 --> 00:12:31,404
Any possible warning
or sense of motivation?

148
00:12:31,538 --> 00:12:32,705
Complete snowjob

149
00:12:32,805 --> 00:12:35,542
Then we went out and told the country
they weren't putting missiles into Cuba

150
